"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/381372","HM Treasury","false","2015-06-23","<p>No final decisions have yet been made as to where regional centres will be located. HM Revenue and Customs are currently considering the options and will make an announcement in due course.</p><p> </p>","South West Hertfordshire","Mr David Gauke","2764 ; 2804 ; 2805 ; 2806","2015-06-23T16:16:26.067Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/381372/answer","Biography information for Mr David Gauke","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/381372/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/381372/answer",,,,,"14","Treasury","Treasury","2015-06-16","Revenue and Customs: Sheffield","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, pursuant to the Answer of 5 June 2015 to Question 196, whether Sheffield is being considered as a Regional Centre office.","false","Biography information for Louise Haigh","Sheffield, Heeley","Louise Haigh","2803"
